## Additional Terms for Story Content

The story content of "Star Trails" is based on real personal experiences and 
is adapted with permission from the original author Sun Yiyang (孙一杨).

While the code is under MIT License, the story content retains copyright to 
the original author. Any commercial use or adaptation of the story content 
should respect and credit the original author.

